_sText:
A simple remake of cs_italy. There were added new areas and new routes are now open for your opponents out of the ambush to do.
	
Unfortunately, my mistakes because of the radar will not be displayed. I have already corrected the error. Those which the map does not want to download times can also fix errors as follows.

cstrike -> resource -> overviews -> de_italy.txt

Here you must just "overviews/de_italy" in "overviews/de_italy_radar change. 



My special thx go to Chizbone for tuning the old Nav file.
